if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_depot')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_depot
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_depot */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_depot (
DepotID int identity,
Name nvarchar(30) not null,
Remark nvarchar(500) null,
depotaddress nvarchar(100) null,
depotzipcode nvarchar(20) null,
depotphone nvarchar(50) null,
IsDel bit not null default 0,
AddTime datetime not null default getdate(),
firstrule int null,
secondrule int null,
thirdrule int null,
constraint PK_BASE_DEPOT primary key (DepotID)
)
go
